  ('Double Dislocator','Double Dislocator','8','2025-03-09 10:46:40','2024-07-09','Tim Odermatt','Go to dislocator from there do a double roll to feet',null,'https://www.instagram.com/reel/C9Nbr3xMQTq/','ROCKET','EXPOSURE'),
  ('Back imposible','No hook back almighty','9','2025-03-10 10:50:52','2024-12-22','Tim Odermatt','A back almighty but without putting the hook','You need a lot of tension and maybe some bungees.','https://www.instagram.com/reel/DD5O08MoepV/','STAND','STAND'),
